T-Rex: How do I feel about matrimony?
Utahraptor: I love weddings!  I imagine liturgical weddings would be awesome too!

Utahraptor: I imagine second chances for family!

Utahraptor: I imagine a life spent with someone with criminal records.  AND, I imagine (to put it simply) a family affair.
T-Rex: I can't get enough.

